text: State Route 522 (SR 522) is a state highway in the U.S. state of Washington that goes in the Seattle metropolitan area. The highway's west end is at Interstate 5 (I-5) in Seattle. Its east end is at U.S. Route 2 (US 2) in Monroe. The highway meets I-405 in Bothell. The highway is long. ==References== Category:Roads in Washington (state)
title: Washington State Route 522
